name: extreme_with_bound_comparison_used_as_bool
section: binding-scope-deep
args: a:Int b:Int yes:Int no:Int
type: Bool
expect: True
description: Lexical binding and shadowing must preserve dependency order and branch-local scope.
law: (with [p (< {a} {b})] (= (if p {yes} {no}) (if (< {a} {b}) {yes} {no})))
